@startuml
title kEmber 分层架构图
caption 参考论文译文与当前工程目录整理的分层总览，按层展示模块，不强调执行时序

top to bottom direction

skinparam backgroundColor #F3F7EE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor white
  BorderColor #2F2F2F
  FontColor #111827
  RoundCorner 0
}

rectangle "命令行 / Demo 调用方" as ExtCaller
rectangle "输入模型文件\nOBJ / STL / Polygon Soup" as ExtInput
rectangle "批处理脚本 / 测试驱动" as ExtScript
rectangle "结果消费者\n可视化 / 下游处理" as ExtOutput

rectangle "用户接口层" #BEEFFF {
  together {
    rectangle "程序入口\nsrc/application/main.cpp" as UI_Main
    rectangle "运行配置 / 参数对象\n任务参数与入口配置" as UI_Config
    rectangle "批处理入口\n测试 / 脚本调用入口" as UI_Batch
    rectangle "结果输出接口\n输出组织与展示入口" as UI_Out
  }
}

rectangle "应用编排层" #EAC7E9 {
  together {
    rectangle "布尔问题装配\nsrc/core/bool_problem.h/.cpp" as APP_Problem
    rectangle "求解任务编排\n输入 polygon 集合组织" as APP_Orchestrate
    rectangle "场景边界计算\ncomputeAABBPlanes()" as APP_AABB
    rectangle "结果汇总\n输出面收集与归并" as APP_Result
    rectangle "任务数据对象\n局部子问题 / 参考状态" as APP_DTO
  }
}

rectangle "核心算法层" #FFE3A8 {
  together {
    rectangle "空间细分\n论文 4.1 / 4.2\n规划实现" as ALG_Subdivision
    rectangle "参考点与 WNV 传播\n论文 4.2.2 / 4.4\n规划实现" as ALG_Ref
    rectangle "局部 BSP 构建\nsrc/algorithm/bsp.h/.cpp" as ALG_BSP
    rectangle "裁剪与交线载体\nsrc/geometry/clipping.h/.cpp" as ALG_Clip
    rectangle "叶面分类\nsegment tracing / f_op(WNV)\n规划实现" as ALG_Classify
  }
}

rectangle "几何领域模型层" #FFDFA8 {
  together {
    rectangle "几何图元\nLine256 / Segment256 / Polygon256\nsrc/geometry/geometry256.h/.cpp" as DOMAIN_Geom
    rectangle "平面点线表示\nPlane3i / HomPoint4i / PlanePoint3i\nsrc/geometry/plane_geometry256.h" as DOMAIN_Plane
    rectangle "绕数与布尔语义\nWNV / BoolStatus / f_diff / f_union\nsrc/math/winding_number.h" as DOMAIN_Winding
    rectangle "局部 BSP 领域对象\nBSPNode / BSPTree" as DOMAIN_BSP
    rectangle "参考点对象\nsrc/algorithm/WNV_tracing.h" as DOMAIN_Ref
  }
}

rectangle "基础设施与数值层" #F4C5D1 {
  together {
    rectangle "文件导入导出适配\nsrc/io/io.h/.cpp\n当前为空壳" as INFRA_IO
    rectangle "整数数学内核\nsrc/math/math256.h" as INFRA_Math
    rectangle "第三方整数实现\ninclude/slimcpplib/*.h" as INFRA_Slim
    rectangle "可选外部几何库\nEigen3 / CGAL\nCMake 可选依赖" as INFRA_3rd
  }
}

database "文件系统" as FS
rectangle "slimcpplib" as SlimLib
rectangle "Eigen3 / CGAL\n可选" as ThirdLib

ExtCaller --> UI_Main
ExtInput --> UI_Config
ExtScript --> UI_Batch
UI_Out --> ExtOutput

UI_Main --> APP_Problem
UI_Config --> APP_Orchestrate
UI_Batch --> APP_Orchestrate
UI_Out --> APP_Result

APP_Problem --> ALG_BSP
APP_Orchestrate --> ALG_Subdivision
APP_Orchestrate --> ALG_BSP
APP_AABB --> ALG_Subdivision
APP_Result --> ALG_Classify
APP_DTO --> ALG_Ref

ALG_Subdivision --> DOMAIN_Geom
ALG_Subdivision --> DOMAIN_Ref
ALG_Ref --> DOMAIN_Ref
ALG_Ref --> DOMAIN_Winding
ALG_BSP --> DOMAIN_BSP
ALG_BSP --> DOMAIN_Geom
ALG_Clip --> DOMAIN_Geom
ALG_Clip --> DOMAIN_Plane
ALG_Classify --> DOMAIN_Winding
ALG_Classify --> DOMAIN_Geom

DOMAIN_Geom --> INFRA_Math
DOMAIN_Plane --> INFRA_Math
DOMAIN_Winding --> INFRA_Math
DOMAIN_BSP --> INFRA_Math
DOMAIN_Ref --> INFRA_Math

INFRA_IO --> FS
INFRA_Math --> INFRA_Slim
INFRA_3rd --> ThirdLib
INFRA_Slim --> SlimLib

APP_Orchestrate --> APP_AABB
APP_Orchestrate --> APP_DTO
APP_Result --> INFRA_IO
UI_Config --> INFRA_IO

note right of ALG_Subdivision
论文定义的完整 EMBER 主流程包含：
空间细分、参考点传播、叶面分类与早停并行。
当前仓库已实装的核心是局部 BSP、裁剪和精确几何内核。
end note

legend right
本图阅读方式：
1. 自上而下看分层职责
2. 同层看模块拆分
3. 箭头仅表示主要依赖方向，不表示执行顺序
endlegend

@enduml
